{
  "stem": "17526.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 68.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was a house with different buildings with one main entrance and inside there was a courtyard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And within the courtyard, you have apartment buildings, two-story apartment buildings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So there was-- this house, so-called house, housed about-- about 10 families maybe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And due to the fact that it was my grandfather's house at one time, so after they have died, it was taken over by the successors, by my mother and my father.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were one of the partners, so to speak, and the rest of the family.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Each one occupied an apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then there were some tenants that paid rent to us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we lived in that house-- I have a picture of this house that was taken it 1974.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was-- is no more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It was not too spacious of a house, but we loved it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was all we knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It was rather primitive compared with today's standards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was no water and no-- there was electricity, but there was an outhouse, there was-- water had to be fetched from the outside.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It wasn't easy, but we didn't-- we were happy with it and so was everybody else.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "This is all we knew and this is we have enjoyed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Thinking back, it's just unbelievable how happy we were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Of course, we were much younger and life that has passed us has been-- we missed, of course.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But we liked it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We liked it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Of course, we have encountered anti-Semitism on every step of the road, but due to the fact that this house had-- this city was strictly populated by Jews, the Jewish population of the city before the war was somewhere between 27,000 and 29,000 people.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
